@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_rgyffr(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.abs((tmp + 0.53 - tmp + 0.61)) * (tmp - 0.20))
    tmp = v0
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.abs((v2 + 0.81 + v0 + 0.09)))
    v2 = (wp.abs((v0 + 0.27 - v0 + 0.30)) * (wp.sin(tmp + 0.28) / v0))
    data[tid] = v0
